    <div class="container">
      <h1>Web Design Hills District</h1>
      <p>Professional website design for businesses in Castle Hill, Bella Vista, Baulkham Hills & surrounding areas</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>Your Local Hills District Web Design Agency</h2>
          <p>Looking for a web designer in the Hills District? Cosmos Web Tech is based right here in Bella Vista, making us the ideal choice for local businesses who want a web design partner they can actually meet face-to-face.</p>

          <p>We understand the Hills District market. From tradies in Castle Hill to healthcare providers in Baulkham Hills, we've helped businesses across the region establish a strong online presence that attracts local customers.</p>

          <h3>Why Choose a Local Web Designer?</h3>
          <ul class="benefits-list">
            <li><strong>Face-to-face meetings</strong> - We can meet at your office or a local cafe to discuss your project</li>
            <li><strong>Local market knowledge</strong> - We understand your customers and competition</li>
            <li><strong>Quick response times</strong> - No offshore delays or time zone issues</li>
            <li><strong>Ongoing support</strong> - We're just a phone call away for any questions</li>
            <li><strong>Community commitment</strong> - We're invested in the success of Hills District businesses</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Web Design Services for Hills District Businesses</h3>
          <p>We offer a full range of web design and digital marketing services:</p>

          <div class="service-boxes">
            <div class="service-box">
              <h4>Business Websites</h4>
              <p>Professional websites that establish credibility and generate leads for your Hills District business.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-box">
              <h4>E-commerce Stores</h4>
              <p>Online stores that let you sell products to customers across Sydney and Australia.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-box">
              <h4>Local SEO</h4>
              <p>Rank higher in Google when Hills District residents search for your services.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-box">
              <h4>Google Ads</h4>
              <p>Targeted advertising to reach potential customers in your local service area.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Suburbs We Serve</h3>
          <p>We work with businesses throughout the Hills District, including:</p>
          <div class="suburbs-grid">
            <ul>
              <li>Bella Vista</li>
              <li>Castle Hill</li>
              <li>Baulkham Hills</li>
              <li>Kellyville</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
              <li>Rouse Hill</li>
              <li>Norwest</li>
              <li>Dural</li>
              <li>Cherrybrook</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
              <li>Glenwood</li>
              <li>Beaumont Hills</li>
              <li>Glenhaven</li>
              <li>The Ponds</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h3>Our Web Design Process</h3>
          <div class="process-simple">
            <div class="process-step">
              <span>1</span>
              <h4>Free Consultation</h4>
              <p>We'll meet (in person or online) to understand your business and goals</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step">
              <span>2</span>
              <h4>Design & Build</h4>
              <p>We create your website and keep you involved every step of the way</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step">
              <span>3</span>
              <h4>Launch & Support</h4>
              <p>We launch your site and provide ongoing support to help you succeed</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Get a Free Quote</h3>
            <p>Contact us today for a free consultation and detailed quote for your Hills District web project.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%;">Request Quote</a>
            <p class="or-call">Or call <a href="tel:0433309677">0433 309 677</a></p>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Starting From</h3>
            <div class="price-display">
              <span class="price">$1,500</span>
              <span class="price-note">for starter websites</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="price-includes">
              <li>5-page website</li>
              <li>Mobile responsive</li>
              <li>Contact form</li>
              <li>Basic SEO setup</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/services/web-design" class="sidebar-link">View all packages →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card highlight">
            <h3>Local to Hills District</h3>
            <p>Our office is located in Bella Vista. We're happy to meet at your place of business or a local cafe.</p>
            <p class="address">
              <strong>Address:</strong><br>
              608/8 Elizabeth Macarthur Dr<br>
              Bella Vista NSW 2153
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta section-navy">
    <div class="container">
